Date: Thu, 16 Nov 2023 21:59:35 +0100
Subject: [PATCH 10/25] net: dsa: mv88e6xxx: Add LED support for 6393X
Organization: Addiva Elektronik

Trigger support:
- "none"
- "timer"
- "netdev"

Signed-off-by: Tobias Waldekranz <tobias@waldekranz.com>
---
